  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Well, as a child, I just know that it was normal.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, in June-- I think it was June, '41-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] no, excuse me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Can I go just back a little bit?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like, during the Russian [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] occupation-- whatever you'd say-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] there was one day, I remember, that a lot of black birds were flying over our village.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were, like, scary, very [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] big birds.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I remember my mother and neighbors were saying something, something terrible is going to happen.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's a bad sign, you know, because of the black birds.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I-- I'm just listening.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I just didn't think nothing at that time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I remember one day I was sitting outside on the porch by the house, sort of all curled up, and these huge German soldiers were marching-- I guess towards the front lines-- and our house was sort of on a main thoroughfare, like main street.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was just sitting there and just sort of, like, amazed to see all these soldiers, you know, and how you put-- with [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] swastikas on their arms.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I wasn't scared.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was just looking at them and just-- thousands, I remember seeing, watching them going by.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this unit, when they went right by me-- and one of the German soldier, he looked at me like where I was sitting and looking at them, and he gave me a big smile, which, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm sure he didn't know I was a Jewish kid.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, of course, I didn't know what was that all about.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I still remember the smile he gave me.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
